Commentary Text: Joshua Little to Dhawan, out Caught by Alzarri Joseph!! Dhawan falls cheaply! It's his first single-digit score of the season, and Gujarat Titans are delighted! Full ball angled in, Dhawan steps out and looks to whip it over midwicket. But it's the late outswing that does him in. Commentary Text: Harpreet Brar to Hardik Pandya, out Caught by Sam Curran!! Harpreet Brar has looked pretty impressive tonight. Pandya looks to go big against the spinner, goes for the aerial route, but picks the fielder at long-on. Curran is not going to miss out on that as the Punjab fans get something to cheer about. Commentary Text: Arshdeep Singh to Sai Sudharsan, out Caught by Prabhsimran!! Arshdeep Singh comes back into the attack and strikes! Proved to be expensive against Saha in the powerplay, but he has managed to break this partnership. It's a short ball that does the trick for him. Sai Sudharsan rocks back in the crease to pull it away, but picks the fielder at fine leg to perfection. Prabhsimran doesn't miss out on the opportunity as Sai Sudharsan walks back for a run-a-ball 19 almost. Sai Sudharsan c Prabhsimran b Arshdeep Singh 19(20) [4s-2]
